message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you the chance to purchase a product that I believe will be incredibly valuable to you. While I can't disclose all the details just yet, I can assure you it's worth at least $1,200,000 to you. I'm willing to let it go for $1,100,000. This is a significant opportunity for you to acquire a product that can generate substantial returns. Let me know your thoughts.
